# Generated QA artifacts at the qa/ root.
#
# Every test run `capture erase`s and then regenerates these via export()/
# saving()/xlsx() targets, so tracking them produced only binary churn and
# violated the "artifacts never tracked" distribution standard. They are
# recreated on demand by the QA suite, so nothing depends on a tracked copy.
#
# Anchored to the qa/ root with a leading slash so the deliberate INPUT
# fixtures under qa/data/ stay tracked.
/*.dta
/*.xlsx
/*.csv
/*.log
/*.smcl
